   <talk_paragraph index="n034_cleric_master_germain-1" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n034_cleric_master_germain-1-a" mid="68" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>What do you mean?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="9"><![CDATA[<html><FONT color=#2b2723>$Master Cleric Jermaine$<BR>Dear brother. You give off a familiar feeling.</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n034_cleric_master_germain-1-a" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n034_cleric_master_germain-1-comp_check" mid="119" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="118"><![CDATA[<html><BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>Master Cleric Jermain camly gazes at you, lost in thought.</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n034_cleric_master_germain-1-b" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n034_cleric_master_germain-1-c" mid="69" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Is it something that concerns… William?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="10"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Cleric Jermain${action:Talk}<BR>May I know what is causing the <FONT color=#a82424>anger</FONT> and sadness within you? I once let myself succumb to the depths of sadness so I would like to be able to help you in any way I can.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n034_cleric_master_germain-1-c" image="QM_GhoulBlue.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n034_cleric_master_germain-1-d" mid="70" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Goddess's plans….</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="11"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Cleric Jermain$<BR>That's right. Although the evil energy of the Death Forest were at works, whenever I think about my master who must have had been tormented in this world… It makes me wonder what plans the Goddess has for us.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n034_cleric_master_germain-1-d" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n034_cleric_master_germain-1-e" mid="71" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="12"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Cleric Jermain$<BR>Humans are easily swayed by darkness. That is the power of balance that the Goddess has given the humans. But it is also the power that makes them weak.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n034_cleric_master_germain-1-e" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n034_cleric_master_germain-1-f" mid="72" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>What should I do?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="13"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Cleric Jermain${action:Talk}<BR>If you can't control the anger that has anchored in your heart, your faith in the Goddess may lose its way .<BR>Like… what happened to my master….</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n034_cleric_master_germain-1-f" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n034_cleric_master_germain-1-g" mid="73" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Where is that?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="14"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Cleric Jermain$<BR>Well, there is no fixed way to <FONT color=#a82424>get out of darkness</FONT>. But there is a place that I always go to whenever I am flooded by sadness.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n034_cleric_master_germain-1-g" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n034_cleric_master_germain-1-h" mid="74" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Will this anger ever go away? I'm my…</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="15"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Cleric Jermain$<BR>Well, it is not some place that has a special meaning.<BR>But if I go up the hill and look at the scenery, I get the feeling that all the bad thoughts in me are disappearing. </html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n034_cleric_master_germain-1-h" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n034_cleric_master_germain-1-party_check1" mid="75" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Please guide me to the place.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_answer link_index="n034_cleric_master_germain-1-j" mid="76" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>I'm not really sure yet.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="16"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Cleric Jermain${action:Talk}<BR>Please do not fear, my brother.<BR>Sadness and fear are all a part of this human world. If you understand that, you will be able to understand the Goddess's power of harmony.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n034_cleric_master_germain-1-i" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_question mid="17"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Cleric Jermain$<BR>Sure. But observing your inner self is something that should be done on your own.<BR>It would be better to leave your companions for a while.<BR><BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>(* You cannot take a Specialization Quest in a party.)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n034_cleric_master_germain-1-j" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_question mid="18"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Cleric Jermain$<BR>It seems like it is too early for you to forget everything. Please come and talk to me again when you have overcome your fears.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n034_cleric_master_germain-1-k" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n034_cleric_master_germain-5" mid="115" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(The hill where you met Jake appears again)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="114"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Cleric Jermain${action:Talk}<BR>It looks like the anger you had inside you is gone and has been replaced with sadness and understanding.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n034_cleric_master_germain-1-l" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n034_cleric_master_germain-1-b" mid="117" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Anger..</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="116"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Cleric Jermain$<BR>I can feel the anger in your eyes that shouldn't be seen from a cleric who serves the Goddess.<BR>
How can you have that anger within you when you are a Goddess's slave?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n034_cleric_master_germain-2" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n034_cleric_master_germain-2-party_check2" mid="77" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Yes. Please guide me.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="19"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Cleric Jermain$<BR>It seems like you could not let go of all that had been bothering you. Do you want to go up the hill again?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n034_cleric_master_germain-2-a" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_question mid="78"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Cleric Jermain$<BR>Sure. But observing your inner self is something that should be done on your own.<BR>It would be better to leave your companions for a while.<BR><BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>(* You cannot take a Specialization Quest in a party.)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n183_cleric_jake-2" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n183_cleric_jake-2-a" mid="79" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>I'm still a little nervous, Cleric Jake.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="20"><![CDATA[<html>$Cleric Jake$<BR>Ah, <FONT color=#387206>{user_nick}</FONT>. <BR>How does it feel to be on your first journey as a Templar Knight?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n183_cleric_jake-2-a" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n183_cleric_jake-2-b" mid="80" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="21"><![CDATA[<html>$Cleric Jake$<BR>Hey… we're the only ones here. You don't have to sound so polite.<BR>Just call me bro like you used to. We are brothers sworn under the Goddess's will.<BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>(Jake is staring at you will friendly eyes)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n183_cleric_jake-2-b" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n183_cleric_jake-2-c" mid="81" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>I'm just following the Goddess's will wherever I go.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="22"><![CDATA[<html>$Cleric Jake$<BR>When we arrive at Mana Ridge and finish our mission, we will be separated to different parts of the world.<BR>Some will go to North, some will go to South... wherever the Goddess's blessing is needed.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n183_cleric_jake-2-c" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n183_cleric_jake-2-d" mid="82" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>I… I just hope everyone will accept Goddess's benevolence….</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="23"><![CDATA[<html>$Cleric Jake$<BR>You're right. We are insignificant beings who are just taking the path laid out by the Goddess. There is no reason or meaning for us to think about it.<BR>But… we are still humans, <FONT color=#387206>{user_nick}</FONT>. Anyone has a little <FONT color=#a82424>dream</FONT> within them.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n183_cleric_jake-2-d" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n183_cleric_jake-2-e" mid="83" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Hmm? You're saying…?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="24"><![CDATA[<html>$Cleric Jake$<BR>Hahaha now is not the time for catechism.<BR>I wasn't expecting an answer that could have come from a stiff new student of the seminary. I was asking about the <FONT color=#a82424>different paths</FONT> of a cleric.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n183_cleric_jake-2-e" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n183_cleric_jake-2-f" mid="84" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Then when will I be choosing the path?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="25"><![CDATA[<html>$Cleric Jake$<BR>You still have some way to go, but soon you will be able to choose which way you are going to take.<BR>The process is usually called <FONT color=#a82424>Specialization</FONT>. </html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n183_cleric_jake-2-f" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n183_cleric_jake-2-g" mid="85" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>The desire to protect….</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="26"><![CDATA[<html>$Cleric Jake$<BR>Our power comes from Goddess's grace.<BR>But what makes our power stronger comes from the <FONT color=#a82424>desire to protect someone</FONT>. Which is ironically a very humanly desire….</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n183_cleric_jake-2-g" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n183_cleric_jake-2-h" mid="88" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Where did you find your fate?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="27"><![CDATA[<html>$Cleric Jake$<BR>Right, you haven't met your fate who needs your protection so all this may sound irrelevant to you. But when you come across that <FONT color=#a82424>fate</FONT>, you will choose your path naturally too.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n183_cleric_jake-2-h" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_question mid="28"><![CDATA[<html>$Cleric Jake$<BR>My <FONT color=#a82424>fate</FONT>? Hahaha…<BR>He's right in front of my eyes. <FONT color=#387206>{user_nick}</FONT>, my precious brother.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1216_cleric_jake-3" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1216_cleric_jake-3-a" mid="91" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Why… Why did you have to make such a choice?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="29"><![CDATA[<html>$Cleric Jake$<BR>I was waiting for you my brother… <BR>My precious brother, <FONT color=#387206>{user_nick}</FONT>.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1216_cleric_jake-3-a" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1216_cleric_jake-3-b" mid="92" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Don't you regret it?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="30"><![CDATA[<html>$Cleric Jake$<BR>That is my <FONT color=#a82424>fate</FONT>. It was my choice. Whether the path shines and sparkles with light, or whether it is a cold and lonely one… if all of it is from the Goddess's will, you will not regret your choice.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1216_cleric_jake-3-b" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1216_cleric_jake-3-c" mid="93" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Jake gently pats your shoulder)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="31"><![CDATA[<html>$Cleric Jake$<BR>What would I regret? Meeting you? Hiding behind the red mask? Or being born a human in this chaotic world…? <FONT color=#387206>{user_nick}</FONT>, I don't regret anything, and you shouldn't too.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1216_cleric_jake-3-c" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1216_cleric_jake-3-d" mid="94" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>How can I forget about the past?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="32"><![CDATA[<html>$Cleric Jake$<BR>My dear brother. I am but a figment of memory to you now. Get it off your mind and walk towards the future.<BR>Nothing can stop you.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1216_cleric_jake-3-d" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1216_cleric_jake-3-e" mid="95" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Jake….</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="33"><![CDATA[<html>$Cleric Jake$<BR>Leave the unforgettable sadness in your heart, and your grudge in your memory.<BR>You will be freed of them someday.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1216_cleric_jake-3-e" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1216_cleric_jake-3-f" mid="96" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="34"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>(Jake doesn't show any sadness on his face.<BR>Did I know that this would be our fate from the beginning…?)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1216_cleric_jake-3-f" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1216_cleric_jake-3-g" mid="97" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>The final thing?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="35"><![CDATA[<html>$Cleric Jake$<BR>It looks like you have regained the strength to take the Goddess's path again. Unlike me, you will be taking the one full of light.<BR>Now is the time to do the final thing.<BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>(Jake has a warm smile on his face)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1216_cleric_jake-3-g" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1216_cleric_jake-3-open_ui3" mid="98" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Choose your path</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="36"><![CDATA[<html>$Cleric Jake$<BR>Overlooking your choice for your future. <BR><BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>* Once selected, the job selection cannot be undone.</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
