      <talk_question mid="89"><![CDATA[<html>$Cleric Jake$<BR>My <FONT color=#a82424>fate</FONT>? Hahaha…<BR>He's right in front of my eyes. <FONT color=#387206>{user_nick}</FONT>, my precious brother.<BR>
<FONT color=#7e12d2>(Jake is smiling happily)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
