      <talk_question mid="37"><![CDATA[<html>$Cleric Jake$<BR>It looks like you're confused. You were always careful in your decisions.<BR>But don't forget that you have to be decisive sometimes.<BR><BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>* Once selected, the job selection cannot be undone.</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
