   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n034_cleric_master_germain-5" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n034_cleric_master_germain-5-a" mid="106" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Yes, I've received a lot of help.</html>]]></talk_answer>
